Relationship adviser and blogger, Joro Olumofin has shared the story of a young man who broke up with his girlfriend in the most awkward way. Rather than insult her or throw her thing out, the duo decided to have good s*x for one last time after crying together and they broke up. The lady also cleaned up his house and walked away. In less than 24 hours, the guy is missing her badly and seeking reconciliation. Read the Nollywood-like drama below: Source